At the moment a change group needs to include the IDs of the statuses, e.g: 

{code}
               "history" : [
                  { "author" : "wseliga", "created": "P1D", "items": [
                     {
                        "fieldType" : "jira",
                        "field" : "status",
                        "from" : "1",
                        "fromString" : "Open",
                        "to" : "5",
                        "toString" : "Resolved"
                     }
                    ]}
{code}

This is unfortunate because it means that this part of the JSON needs to be pre-processed in our Sample data importer (because we can't pre-know the IDs for the statuses in our workflow). 

JIM obviously has the functionality to work this out already because in the issue itself the 'status' field is magically converted to the right ID.

