Comparing with the sample JSON data which is generated when we export an issue to JSON, the mentioned user details are included in the JSON:
{noformat}
  "users" : [ {
    "name" : "admin",
    "fullname" : "admin",
    "email" : "admin@mail.com",
    "groups" : [ "jira-users", "jira-administrators", "jira-developers" ],
    "active" : true
  } ]
{noformat}

Hence, it will be great if we are able to provide a complete JSON data example that our customers can refer to.

